main event: A witness reported seeing a class D flying saucer near Springfield, Ohio on June 11, 1967.
interesting points: The observer was parked in the woods with others when he spotted the object,The object was approximately 100 ft in diameter and metallic in color,The observer described hearing sonar-like sounds before looking up to see the object,The witness appeared nervous and evasive when contacted by the officer,No photographs or physical evidence were reported.
witness description: A nervous male who was reluctant to provide further information.
